BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: try	set status to do shell script "ps -eo etime,args|grep '[[:space:]]caffeinate[[:space:]]'|grep -v grep"on error	set status to ""end tryif status = "" then	do shell script "caffeinate -d > /dev/null 2>&1 &"	return "on"else	do shell script "killall -9 caffeinate"	return "off"end if

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: try	do shell script "ps -eo etime,args|grep '[[:space:]]caffeinate[[:space:]]'|grep -v grep"	set status to "on"on error	set status to "off"end try
